caption.p: Expression of cytokines in human cells infected with reassortant avian influenza viruses (AIVs). Human A549 cells were infected by reassortant AIVs at a multiplicity of infection (MOI) of 0.1. Total IFN-α, IFN-β, and TNF-α RNA were extracted at (A) 6 and (B) 12 hpi, and cytokines were quantified by qRT-PCR.
